graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelMesh -->|distributed coordination<br/>model registry| etcd[etcd v3.5+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMesh -->|model storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>AWS S3, MinIO<br/>REQUIRED*]
    ModelMesh -->|model storage| PVC[PersistentVolume<br/>REQUIRED*]
    ModelMesh -->|cluster orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelMesh -.->|certificate management| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.55+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMesh -.->|traffic management| Istio[Istio<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|CRD definitions| KServe[KServe<br/>ServingRuntime, InferenceService CRDs]
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| ModelMesh
    ODHOp[ODH/RHOAI Operator] -->|installation & config| ModelMesh

    %% Integration Points
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics<br/>8443/TCP, 2112/TCP| ModelMesh
    ServiceMesh[Service Mesh] -.->|mTLS, traffic routing| ModelMesh

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|inference runtimes| MLServer[MLServer<br/>sklearn, xgboost, lightgbm]
    ModelMesh -->|inference runtimes| Triton[Triton Inference Server<br/>tensorflow, pytorch, onnx]
    ModelMesh -->|inference runtimes| OVMS[OpenVINO Model Server<br/>openvino_ir, onnx]
    ModelMesh -->|inference runtimes| TorchServe[TorchServe<br/>pytorch-mar]

    %% Notes
    Note1[*Either S3 or PersistentVolume required]

